OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSir Derek Jacobi warns of  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'elitist' theatre prices   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sir Derek Jacobi has said he's         
OL,6, "shocked" by high West End ticket      
OL,7, prices, which risk making theatre an   
OL,8, "elitist" pursuit.                     
OL,10,FThe acting great, 84, received the     
OL,11,Flifetime achievement award at the      
OL,12,FOlivier Awards in London on Sunday.    
OL,14,FHe was quoted by the Guardian as saying
OL,15,F"it was much easier" to see plays      
OL,16,Fcheaply when he first started out.     
OL,18,FThere's an ongoing debate about whether
OL,19,Fsome fans are priced out of the theatre
OL,20,Fduring the cost of living crisis.      
